      </row>
      <row>
        <cell> New York </cell>
        <cell> 19,651,127 </cell>
      </row>

    </tabular>
  </table>
  <p>And the three smallest are:</p>
  <table>
    <tabular>

      <row header="yes">
        <cell> State </cell>
