  </table>
  <p>The three largest states in land area are Alaska, Texas, and California. The three smallest are Connecticut,
    Delaware, and Rhode Island.</p>
  <p>The three <em>richest</em> states (by per capita income) are Maryland, Alaska, and New Jersey. The three poorest
    are Arkansas, West Virginia, and Mississippi.</p>
